<td width="auto" height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #ff9900; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;"><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">Find your Ski Holiday</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Skiing Requirements</h2>
<p>To join our Meet the Pistes ski hosting sessions, all we ask is that you can ski red runs confidently, but you do not need to be an 'advanced' skier. No instruction is given - that is strictly for the local ski school - but this is a great way to get a knowledgeable overview of the area, meet your Rep and fellow guests, and enjoy a great ski day out!</p>
</div>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Where can you Meet the Pistes?</h2>
<p>Our Meet the Pistes Services is available in resorts with an Inghams rep in <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland"><strong>Switzerland</strong></a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy"><strong>Italy</strong></a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra"><strong>Andorra</strong> </a>and most of <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria"><strong>Austria</strong> </a>with the full details being supplied on arrival from your resort Rep. In Canada a local ski host will offer a similar service.</p>
<p>Check our resort pages to see Meet the Pistes availability in your resort!</p>
</div>
